cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SC, cs.CC, cs.NA. 

This paper involves distributed computation on a large scale using Apache Hadoop clusters, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The computation also involves handling and processing large amounts of data, which could fall under Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The elastic computation framework developed for scheduling computation slices based on changing cluster load condition could fall under Scalable Computing (cs.SC). The MapReduce program used for computation could fall under Computation and Language (cs.CL). Finally, the use of numerical methods and algorithms for computing Pi could fall under Numerical Analysis (cs.NA).
